    "body": "### Problem\n\n[This blog post](https://zed.dev/blog/zed-decoded-vim) detailed some issues with trying to embed Neovim into another editor that may be relevant.\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nNeovim should be customisable enough when embedded to allow the widest range of usecases. ",
